query:
SELECT id AS id,
       jurisdiction_id AS jurisdiction_id,
       geojson AS geojson
FROM
  (SELECT id,
          jurisdiction_id,
          jsonb_build_object('type', 'Feature', 'id', id, 'geometry', ST_AsGeoJSON(geometry)::jsonb, 'properties', to_jsonb(row) - 'id' - 'geometry') AS geojson
   FROM structures row) AS expr_qry
WHERE jurisdiction_id = '3951'
LIMIT 10000;
